00:04:08.210 --> 00:04:09.032
Don't be reckless.

00:04:13.291 --> 00:04:13.851
Go back.

00:04:17.691 --> 00:04:18.210
Really?

00:04:19.931 --> 00:04:20.491
Trust me.

00:04:21.491 --> 00:04:22.450
I'm the chosen one.

