00:04:35.330 --> 00:04:36.530
The moonlight is beautiful.

00:04:36.931 --> 00:04:38.410
Won't you stay and admire it?

00:04:41.691 --> 00:04:42.171
Get lost.

00:04:50.931 --> 00:04:52.171
(You're not cold-blooded.)

00:04:53.410 --> 00:04:55.210
